{"tid":1664221,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（熱烈地彈琴）智利政府撤回地鐵加價","createTime":"2019-10-20T03:07:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T04:10:03.000Z","uid":183971,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"113e85dc4934273c3ab21596ad4f2b6f402ffcdb","tid":1664221,"uid":183971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:07:26.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】智利因應地鐵加價引發的示威，在首都聖地亞哥實施宵禁並撤回加價。<br />\n<br />\n軍方在聖地亞哥街頭施放水炮及催淚彈驅散示威者，示威者拒絕撤離，繼續跟士兵對峙，又焚燒雜物築起防線。<br />\n<br />\n多架巴士被燒成廢鐵，最少70個地鐵站受破壞。營運公司估計損失達二千萬美元，暫時未知鐵路服務能否在周一恢復。<br />\n<br />\n智利早前先加電費一成，之後再將繁忙時段地鐵車資調高近百分之四，觸發民眾激烈示威，令聖地亞哥進入緊急狀態。<br />\n<br />\n軍方接管首都治安是智利1990年結束軍事獨裁以來，首次有士兵巡邏聖地亞哥街頭，並宣布晚上10時至早上7時宵禁。<br />\n<br />\n起初批評示威者搞破壞的總統皮涅拉態度軟化，宣布撤回地鐵加價，指民主是由虛心聆聽民眾訴求來建立，亦會制定特別法例，檢討地鐵車資。"},{"pid":"adb86c869778f78bb87fa7872f6a1225e2c5deb1","tid":1664221,"uid":183971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:10:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇學習地方？"},{"pid":"7fc5cbb5613a0c025fc884c1aae28c1b7a17d669","tid":1664221,"uid":165336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:26:02.000Z","msg":"人地加下價都搞到咁<br />\n黨鐵俾支共控制,亂咁封站又放狗打人<br />\n而家打爛小小野,港豬廢老就嘈到拆天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdbbff8071a09e3d89a591b0750923971488027a","tid":1664221,"uid":183971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fc5cbb5613a0c025fc884c1aae28c1b7a17d669","tid":1664221,"uid":165336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:26:02.000Z","msg":"人地加下價都搞到咁<br />\n黨鐵俾支共控制,亂咁封站又放狗打人<br />\n而家打爛小小野,港豬廢老就嘈到拆天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:26:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d03a27b4d1abd1596fee00acbb7c3e6fa090c52","tid":1664221,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:35:22.000Z","msg":"加左十二次唔火有鬼"},{"pid":"b4b394deeb1f91062579ee5f29a1043e2121406e","tid":1664221,"uid":183971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4d03a27b4d1abd1596fee00acbb7c3e6fa090c52","tid":1664221,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:35:22.000Z","msg":"加左十二次唔火有鬼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:36:13.000Z","msg":"地鐵有加冇減機制都加左好多次了"},{"pid":"f9208b122ea97bb6a19ac4ee83be7f8cca9e0ff2","tid":1664221,"uid":183971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:52:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f24ae53520541c40da23f26ca5fc208567df91ad","tid":1664221,"uid":183971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:55:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aad776f021b21283fa14c1045ec828fc993597af","tid":1664221,"uid":183971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:57:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"586890959b495e5a79d310c89d99754043b8da7b","tid":1664221,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:58:47.000Z","msg":"恭喜智利人民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ac4bce8ed338d3d34ddbbfe64abfde18c2e5f58","tid":1664221,"uid":183971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"586890959b495e5a79d310c89d99754043b8da7b","tid":1664221,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2